node.text:
I’m proud of who I am. Who I’ve grown to be. Even in all my imperfections.

This isn’t a “self made“ story…. all of the life experiences and the people in my life who helped me grow to where I am today. 

Every moment, every memory, every person, even every failure…The energy, love, friendships, this community ….has brought me life lessons, highs & lows, successes, and GROWTH. 

I have ALWAYS wanted to share this journey and knowledge with YOU, and we did just that with @thejillyacademy ! 

So today I am thrilled to announce that our @thejillyacademy Fall Semester is back in session!! 

This online educational platform covers digital marketing, brand strategy, monetizing your online buisness and so much more! Are you ready to take that leap of faith to invest in yourself? 

With a new season upon us I am ready to reboot, refocus and reinvigorate and can’t wait for you to join me in getting after our goals, creating our own magic and making our dreams come true! 

See you in class!
Xo

node.text: When we first took possession of the farm, I wasn't planning on touching the farmhouse with a ten-foot pole 🤪, but after a few glasses of wine, my family convinced me give this little farmhouse some love… and next thing I knew I was picking out paint colours and the demo was underway! In this episode, we're talking all about the demo, paint, and furnishings! Are you enjoying our farmhouse refresh mini-series? Let us know below! @justinpasutto …. Great cameos @cwpersona ♥️

That’s right!!! 

We recently announced over on @thejillyacademy that SCHOOL’S OUT FOR SUMMER! From July 6th-August 31st we are closing up shop to give the Alumni the time and space to work through the courses and truly work on implementing their learnings.

Have you been thinking about joining the Alumni community?! Now is the time to take that leap of faith and invest in yourself! Make your purchase TODAY so you don’t miss out until September! (Link in profile) 

And DON’T WORRY! Team Jilly isn’t going anywhere! Customer service will still be available to you whenever you need it! If you already have purchased the courses you will NOT lose access and can complete the courses when it works best for YOU! 

We want everyone to take this summer to really focus on nurturing the relationships in your life on and OFF screen and of course give yourself space for lots of self care! Take your learnings to the cottage, city park, favourite cafe… anywhere that is your happy place! 

I will say that this will be no ordinary summer for #TheJillyAcademy though… Follow along on our social channels to stay tuned! Get ready for a summer filled with growth, positivity, and of course FUN! 💗

node.text: You guys!! @justinpasutto and I have literally been chomping at the bit, pun intended… To bring you along this journey and new adventure of ours! When grandma MARGE was alive, she would always tell me that she wishes I would just get married, I have babies, and move to a farm… If only she could see me now 😭😭😭. Justin and I have absolutely no clue what we’re doing, what we’re gonna farm, and what this is going to look like… But we are so up for the challenge, i’m so so so so excited to bring you all along with us!

It's THYME to give back to your local charities!  🌱 Last week, the girls on Team Jilly and I had the pleasure of visiting the @mamasformamas farm. We helped them weed the field and plant some new seeds to get ready for the season ahead. For me, there is truly no better feeling than giving back to my local community!

Do you love giving back? Well, guess what? You can do just that and win $10,000 for the charity of YOUR choice! @telus has just launched their Friendly Future Days month of giving with a $100K social contest to inspire you to give back to your local community. From now until May 31st, you can win one of ten $10K donations to YOUR charity of choice!

How to enter:
1. Comment on @telus’s #FriendlyFuture Days contest-related posts on Facebook or Instagram explaining how you or a friend is giving back to your community.
OR
2. Create and post an image, or a video on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, or TikTok explaining how you or a friend is giving back to your community, using the hashtag #FriendlyFuture

Good luck! I can't wait to see which charities receive these extremely generous donations 🥰

node.text: I can’t think of a group of people to be more grateful for and respectful to. The people who brought our babies into the world. Who saved both of my parents from heart attacks. Who cared for my granny year in and year out…. Who made my dad feel like everything was going to be ok throughout his cancer treatments. Took care of my babe with his busted ankle. The humans that were there with open hearts when we said goodbye to our grandparents. Delivered all my favourite nieces and nephews. Helped our family through moms debilitating depression for YEARS, and NEVER gave up until she got better. We never thought she would get better. Now she’s better than EVER.  BECAUSE OF HEALTHCARE WORKERS. Doctors. Scientists. Nurses. Janitors. Lab Techs. Pharmacists. Paramedics (list goes on)….We trusted these humans with our LIVES… and I’ll continue to trust them with my life… I’d say they’ve done a pretty good job so far.  Proud to be vaccinated. Proud to trust the pros and grateful for their endless hours, dedication, hard work and LOVE. 😷❤️‍🩹🧑🏼‍⚕️👩🏽‍🔬🥼🚑🔬🦠💉💊🧪❤️ TO ALL HEALTH CARE WORKERS READING THIS. THANK. YOU. 🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼

I’m proud of who I am. Who I’ve grown to be. Even in all my imperfections.

This isn’t a “self made“ story…. all of the life experiences and the people in my life who helped me grow to where I am today. 

Every moment, every memory, every person, even every failure…The energy, love, friendships, this community ….has brought me life lessons, highs & lows, successes, and GROWTH. 

I have ALWAYS wanted to share this journey and knowledge with YOU, and we did just that with @thejillyacademy ! 

So today I am thrilled to announce that our @thejillyacademy Fall Semester is back in session!! 

This online educational platform covers digital marketing, brand strategy, monetizing your online buisness and so much more! Are you ready to take that leap of faith to invest in yourself? 

With a new season upon us I am ready to reboot, refocus and reinvigorate and can’t wait for you to join me in getting after our goals, creating our own magic and making our dreams come true! 

See you in class!
Xo

I can’t believe it’s almost time for the fall season!! As I’m reflecting back on this summer, I am so grateful for the beautiful memories with my family and friends. I took more time off to step back and slow down. I was able to spend so much time with the kids and made the most of Leo’s last summer before he goes to SCHOOL! 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
With this new season around the corner, I am ready to reboot, switch gears, and revisit my goals leading into the end of the year. September, to me, has always been a chance to refocus and get down to business! Whether that means taking on new projects, launching new products, or going back to school! 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
And speaking of school... Fall Semester is ONE WEEK AWAY for @thejillyacademy …. I am so excited for the relaunch of the first three courses on September 1st! Are you ready to take that leap of faith and invest in yourself? Let’s make September all about finding your WHY and investing in yourself to truly make your dreams come true! 💗. … thank you @justinpasutto for capturing this pic 😭🥰🙏🏼
